        {
            "title": "短炒波士｜港股料續區間上落 黃金仍有短炒優勢｜Ringo",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pObsmA.mOcv9rGoP3leWCA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bossmind_356/5634147b510a7d491b7cb94fab5f6a45\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股日前曾衝穿兩萬六，惟未能企穩。恒指預期繼續在區間範圍24800點至26400點之間上落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">騰訊（700）周三收市後公布業績。由於該股的透明度高，故業績後股價出現大幅異動的機會較低，短期阻力位介乎560元至580元。若已持貨的投資者仍擔心業績或令市場失望而出現下跌，可部署少量的熊證或買入認沽期權（Long Put）作風險管理。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">汽車股近日有反彈，比亞迪（1211）亦回升至100元水平。該股近3個月在低位橫行整固，料大致已完成築底，若跌穿85元才須擔心有另一輪跌勢。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-66e01794-f389-3375-b428-83034d41fb14-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滙控（005）自近期高位跌約一成半（計及除淨）。然而，現價股息率仍未算特別嚟引，若跌至116元至117 元才考慮也不遲，短期上方阻力位在130元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金價近期在每盎司5,000美元附近上落，具有短炒優勢。短期上望5,070至5,080美元，下方在4,970附近止蝕。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣近日已重上7萬美元水平，可考慮在7.8萬美元止賺，下方支持位繼續在6萬美元不變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Ringo<br/>資深投資者<br/>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://signup.hkiei.com/ringo_webinar_bossmind\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"686\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aouFIvgBhvOtOKgFyoB7aA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bossmind_356/f52012128630469615370091d56ff897\" width=\"960\"/></div></a></div>",
